metadata.name: Invictus Order #1
metadata.description:
As a part of the Invictus Order, you have enlisted to join the Sector Task Force, an elite squad established to solve the mystery of The Altar. With 79 completely unique base models, Invictus Order is one of the most dynamic collections ever created.

By owning an Invictus Order, you are automatically agreeing to the [Invictus Order Ownership Agreement](https://www.invictusorder.com/ownership_agreement).
